comment: Horford (ATL) contests the shot by Thompson (PHI), making "high-five" contact with his hand after the release of the shot, which is legal.
Even though he is moving backwards, Canaan (PHI) establishes himself in Teague's (ATL) path and is legal when the contact occurs.
Smith (PHI) does not establish himself in Bazemore's (ATL) path, but is coming in from an angle when the contact occurs.
Scott (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive by Canaan (PHI).
Teague (ATL) makes contact with Noel's (PHI) arm as he makes a move toward the basket.
